from java.lang import Class,String
from java.lang import ClassLoader
from java.net import URLClassLoader,URL
from java.sql import DriverManager
from jarray import zeros, array

#MODIFY THIS SECTION to set the details for your GA query

tableName = 'toparticles'
description = 'GA table with Ad Content'
dimensions = 'pagePath'
metrics = 'users,pageviews,timeonpage,sessions'
profile = '163656644'

#DONT MODIFY BELOW
outputFolder = '/usr/share/tomcat8/api_profiles/Google%20Analytics/'
rtk = ''

# The directory to search
path = '/usr/share/java/cdata/cdata.jdbc.googleanalytics/'

#the below is used to get the latest jar
# Build a list of the subdirectories of directory path
dirs = [os.path.join(path, dir) for dir in os.listdir(path)
                    if os.path.isdir(os.path.join(path,dir))]

# Sorted them in reverse order (largest alphabetically first)
# and extract the first (largest) entry
newest = sorted(dirs,reverse=True)[0]

#print(newest)

#now get jar from that dir
jars = []
for root, dirs, files in os.walk(newest):
    for file in files:
        if file.endswith('.jar'):
            jars.append(file)
jar = jars[0]

#print jar

myarray = array([URL("file://"+newest+"/"+jar)], URL)

loader = URLClassLoader(myarray, ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader());

SELECT u.id as user_id, u.client_id, u.username, u.password as pw_hash, secQ.questions[1] as question_one,
       secQ.questions[2] as question_two, secQ.answers[1] as answer_one, secQ.answers[2] as answer_two
FROM (
  	SELECT s.oidc_rp_client_id as client_id, x.id, x.username, x.password
  	from (
  		SELECT auth.id, profile.site_id,
  			CASE WHEN profile.migrated_username != ''
  				Then profile.migrated_username
  				else auth.username
  				end as username,
  			auth.password
    	from auth_user as auth, profiles_userprofile as profile
  		where auth.id=profile.user_id and not auth.is_staff and not auth.is_superuser) as x
  	left join gem_oidcsettings as s on s.site_id=x.site_id) as u
left join (
  	SELECT user_id, array_agg(answer) as answers, array_agg(question) as questions
  	from (
      	select a.user_id, a.answer, q.question
      	from profiles_securityanswer as a, (
          	select question_id, json_object(array_agg(locale), array_agg(title)) as question
				from (
  					select distinct(p.title), t.question_id, l.locale
  					from (
      					select distinct(translated_page_id), question_id
      					from profiles_securityanswer
      					left join core_pagetranslation on page_id=question_id) as t,
  					wagtailcore_page as p, core_sitelanguage as l, core_languagerelation as r
  					where (p.id=t.translated_page_id or p.id=t.question_id) and r.page_id=p.id and r.language_id=l.id
  					order by l.locale) as a
				group by question_id) as q
      	where a.question_id=q.question_id
      	order by a.user_id, q.question_id desc) as x
  	group by user_id) as secQ
On u.id=secQ.user_id

select question_id, json_object(array_agg(locale), array_agg(title))
from (
  	select distinct(p.title), t.question_id, l.locale
  	from (
      	select distinct(translated_page_id), question_id
      	from profiles_securityanswer

  	where (p.id=t.translated_page_id or p.id=t.question_id) and r.page_id=p.id and r.language_id=l.id

cursor.execute("Select Distinct episodeid, episodename From girleffect.gc_tbl_EpisodeIdDetails")
episodes = cursor.fetchall()

stg_table = 'gc_stg_episodes'
prd_table = 'gc_tbl_episodes_summary'
columns = ['rc_weekcom DATE NULL']
col_names = ['rc_weekcom']

# get Episode names for the table columns
for episode in episodes:
  col_names.append(episode[1])
  columns.append('"{}" INT NULL'.format(episode[1]))

# create Staging table
sql = """
	DROP TABLE IF EXISTS "girleffect"."{0}" CASCADE;
	CREATE TABLE "girleffect"."{0}" ({1})
""".format(stg_table, ','.join(sorted(columns)))
cursor.execute(sql)

# Create prod episodes summary table
sql = """
	CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "girleffect"."{0}" ({1});
""".format(prd_table, ','.join(sorted(columns)))

sql = """
SELECT Distinct rc_weekcom, episodename, COUNT(rc_weekcom)
FROM girleffect.gc_sq_base
INNER JOIN girleffect.gc_tbl_EpisodeIdDetails ON gc_sq_base.rc_amended_EpId = gc_tbl_EpisodeIdDetails.EpisodeId
GROUP BY rc_weekcom, episodename
ORDER BY rc_weekcom, episodename
"""

cursor.execute(sql)
results = cursor.fetchall()
values = {}
sql_vals = []
str_sql_vals = ''   
sql = "INSERT INTO girleffect.{} ({}) VALUES ".format(
  stg_table,
  ','.join(['"{}"'.format(x) for x in sorted(col_names)]))

for item in results:
  if str(item[0]) not in values.keys():
  	values.update({str(item[0]): {}})
  values[str(item[0])]['rc_weekcom'] = item[0]  
  values[str(item[0])][item[1]] = item[2]

  
for row in [v for v in sorted(values.values())]:
  item = []
  for col in sorted(col_names):
    if col in row.keys():
      if not col == 'rc_weekcom':
        item.append(str(row[col]) if row[col] != None else 'null')
      else:
        item.append("'{}'".format(row[col].strftime('%m-%d-%Y')))
    else:
      item.append('null')
    sql_vals.append(item)
    
for i in sql_vals:
  str_sql_vals += '({}),'.format(','.join(i))

cursor.execute(sql + str_sql_vals[0:len(str_sql_vals)-1])

CASE
WHEN level='Brand level' THEN typeperson || location || schooled

CASE
WHEN level='Product level' THEN number
WHEN level='Brand level' THEN
	CASE
	WHEN number_summed is null THEN 0
	ELSE number_summed
	END
END

CASE
WHEN level='Product level' THEN population
ELSE FIRST_VALUE (population IGNORE NULLS) OVER
(PARTITION BY "segment_lookup"rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following)
END

CASE
WHEN level='Product level' THEN country
ELSE (Select country from  stg_nnos_product limit 1)
END

CASE
WHEN level='Brand level' THEN category
ELSE measure
END

CASE
WHEN category='Awareness' THEN SUM ("number") OVER
(PARTITION BY segment_lookup, awareness is not null rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following)
WHEN category='Reach' THEN SUM ("number") OVER
(PARTITION BY segment_lookup, reach is not null rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following)
WHEN category='Regular Reach' THEN SUM ("number") OVER
(PARTITION BY segment_lookup, regular_reach is not null rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following)
WHEN category='Multiregular Reach' THEN SUM ("number") OVER
(PARTITION BY segment_lookup, multiregular_reach is not null rows between unbounded preceding and unbounded following)
ELSE "number"
END

CASE

ELSE number

SELECT
  CASE
WHEN  Max("rc_telephoneid") is null
THEN 1
WHEN "rc_telephoneid" is null 
THEN Max("rc_telephoneid") +1 
END AS "rc_telephoneid", 
  "rc_clinumber", 
  "firstcall", 
  "firstweek" 
FROM $T{tbl_telenumbers}
group by "rc_telephoneid", "rc_clinumber", "firstcall", "firstweek"
order by "rc_telephoneid", "rc_clinumber", "firstcall", "firstweek"

CASE DATEPART(WEEKDAY, "startdate")  
    WHEN 0 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -6, "startdate") -- 'SUNDAY' 
    WHEN 1 THEN "startdate" -- 'MONDAY' 
    WHEN 2 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -1, "startdate") -- 'TUESDAY' 
    WHEN 3 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -2, "startdate") -- 'WEDNESDAY' 
    WHEN 4 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -3, "startdate") -- 'THURSDAY' 
    WHEN 5 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -4, "startdate") -- 'FRIDAY' 
    WHEN 6 THEN DATEADD(DAY, -5, "startdate") -- 'SATURDAY' 
END

CASE
  WHEN 
  	("clinumber" is null or "clinumber" = '') AND LEN("registerid") > 6
  THEN  RIGHT("registerid", 10)
  ELSE RIGHT("clinumber", 10)
END

CASE
  WHEN 
  	UPPER("disconnectreasion") = 'NONWORKINGHOUR'
    OR
    "accessservice" = '00|0000'
    OR
    "accessservice" = '00'
    OR 
    "exitlocation" = '0000'
    OR 
    "exitlocation" = '00'
    OR 
    "exitlocation" = '0'
  THEN 'NA'
  ELSE "language" 
END

CASE
  WHEN 
    "rc_clinumber" IN (SELECT "testnumber" FROM "girleffect"."gc_tbl_testclinumbers")
    OR (
      LEN("rc_clinumber") > 0  AND (LEN("rc_clinumber") < 7 OR LEN("rc_clinumber") > 10)
    )
    OR 
    "ucid" is null OR "ucid" = ''
    OR
    "rc_clinumber" is null OR "rc_clinumber" = ''
  THEN TRUE
  ELSE FALSE
END

CASE
  WHEN 
      LEN("rc_clinumber") > 0
      AND LOWER("rc_clinumber") != 'anonymous'
      AND LEN("registerid") < 8 
      AND "rc_exclude" = False
  THEN CAST("registerid" AS INT)
  ELSE NULL
END

CASE
  WHEN 
  	"exit_type" is null
  THEN "count"
END

SELECT 
date_trunc('day', m.created_on) as day_sent,
count(distinct(m.contact_id))
FROM girleffect.rpp_tbl_flows_flowrun as fr
LEFT JOIN girleffect.rpp_tbl_flows_flowstep AS fs ON fr.id = fs.run_id
LEFT JOIN girleffect.rpp_tbl_flows_flowstep_messages AS fs_m ON fs_m.flowstep_id = fs.id
LEFT JOIN girleffect.rpp_tbl_msgs_msg AS m ON fs_m.msg_id = m.id
WHERE fr.flow_id = 82
AND m.direction = 'I'

GROUP BY day_sent
ORDER BY day_sent

SELECT 
    a.timestamp as day_sent,
    sum(a.count) as responses,
    a.flow_id
FROM (
    SELECT
    fpc.period as timestamp,
    fpc.count as count,
    fpc.from_uuid,
    fpc.flow_id,
    rsu.uuid
  	FROM girleffect.rpp_stg_ruleset_uuid as rsu
    LEFT JOIN girleffect.rpp_tbl_flows_flowpathcount as fpc ON fpc.from_uuid = u.uuid
) as a
GROUP BY day_sent, a.flow_id
Order BY day_sent
